title: No. 22 Temple pulls away late to beat East Carolina 24-14
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
P.J. Walker threw a late 23-yard touchdown pass to Robby Anderson, and No. 22 Temple rallied to beat East Carolina 24-14 on Thursday night. ...
